Neotice

We are excited to announce that the beta version of the [ **Neotice**
](https://www.neotice.app) app, which is the production version of NewsGPT, is
now available for users to try out! We are grateful to the Streamlit Hackathon
for showcasing our prototype and philosophy. With the help of this platform,
we are confident that our app will revolutionize the way people consume news.
